# Load Packages

```{r}
library(readr)
library(here)
library(tidyverse)
```

# Load Data

```{r}
clinical_sample <- read.delim(here("data", "data_clinical_sample.txt"), sep = "\t", skip = 4, header = TRUE)
```

```{r}
clinical_sample |>
  select(-c(PATIENT_ID, SAMPLE_ID))|>
  summarise_all(unique)
```
